      "text": "The contract is listed under one of their subsidiary companies, [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGoldenStarEntertainmentGroup],Golden Star Entertainment]], and it is standard [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMRB],MRB]] escort, although with a couple additional clauses regarding the participation of our MechWarriors to operate '[[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHolovid],holovid]] 'Mech props'.\n\nThere appears to be nothing extraordinary with this contract Dr. Murad.",
